                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Seems like a classic bait and switch -- you know go to a store to buy a high def color TV.  Salesman tells you about how great their cust. service is -- any problem you have we will be right there with you to help fix. So you put money down and order one.
<br />

<br />
Months later you get a delivery -- you open the package with anticipation and find -- a B/W TV circa 1975.  You call the salesman "This is not a nerf."
<br />

<br />
Ok tell me I am way off base here, but did they not promise our involvement in how the direction of the chanter class will progress.
<br />

<br />
Who here would have bought OOW with the changes made to chanters?
<br />

<br />
It is obvious from Brenlo's statements, SOE has no intention of listening to this community.  Therefore our only recourse may be a legal one.
<br />

<br />
Note:  quitting does nothing to the general community at large.  As many have stated before -- there are plenty of buff bots at large.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
